text = "[b]Chess pieces[/b]
JohnPablok's improved Cburnett set (CC0), based on a design by Colin M. L. Burnett.
[url=https://opengameart.org/content/chess-pieces-and-board-squares]opengameart.org[/url]

[b]Emoji & icons[/b]
All emojis designed by OpenMoji, the open-source emoji and icon project. License: CC BY-SA 4.0.
[url=https://openmoji.org]openmoji.org[/url]

[b]Typeface[/b]
OpenDyslexic: a free, dyslexia-friendly font.
[url=https://opendyslexic.org]opendyslexic.org[/url]

[b]Chess engine[/b]
Stockfish (GPL-3.0).

[b]Puzzles[/b]
Lichess Open Database (CC0).
[url=https://database.lichess.org]database.lichess.org[/url]

[b]Built with[/b]
Godot Engine (MIT). [url=https://godotengine.org]godotengine.org[/url]

[b]Source & licenses[/b]
[url=https://github.com/Hatscat/limpidchess]https://github.com/Hatscat/limpidchess[/url]"
